  "body": "<div id=\"post-view220019159607\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea220019159607\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><strong>※ 자동차보험으로 한방치료가 가능하다?!</strong></span></p><p><span style='font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; background-color: rgb(246, 243, 145);'><strong><br /></strong></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140603_145/isuhani_1401765163445NK9Mg_JPEG/%BB%E7%B0%ED3.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"326\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rheight: 326px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140603_145/isuhani_1401765163445NK9Mg_JPEG/%BB%E7%B0%ED3.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333A29F237')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140603_145/isuhani_1401765163445NK9Mg_JPEG/%BB%E7%B0%ED3.jpg?type=w3\"></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'>자동차손해배상보장법 개정 이후 교통사고 후유증 치료비 전액을 자동차보험으로 처리가능합니다.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">자동차보험치료는 정형외과 입원치료 및 물리치료만 보험적용이 되는것으로 알고 계신분들이 많으실텐데요..&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt;\"><u>침이나 뜸,부항 추나요법 및 한약처방까지 통원치료에 관한 비용도 한의원에서 자동차보험 혜택을 받을 수 있습니다.</u></span></strong></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style='font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>&nbsp;</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140603_174/isuhani_14017659410605UIhl_JPEG/%B1%C3%B1%DD.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"50\" height=\"84\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 84px; rwidth: 50px;\" id=\"20140603_174/isuhani_14017659410605UIhl_JPEG/%B1%C3%B1%DD.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333A29F237')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140603_174/isuhani_14017659410605UIhl_JPEG/%B1%C3%B1%DD.jpg?type=w3\">&nbsp;<span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; background-color: rgb(255, 167, 0);'><strong>자동차보험, 이것이 궁금하다!</strong></span></div><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;'>&nbsp;</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><u><span style='color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'><u><strong>- 한의원에서도 자동차보험으로 치료를 받을 수 있나요?</strong></u></span></u></p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'>네, 가능합니다. 한의원의 다양한 치료가&nbsp; 자동차보험으로 전액보상받으실 수 있기 때문에 본인부담금 없이 자동차보험으로 한방치료가 가능합니다.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><u><span style='color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'><u>- </u></span><span style='color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'><u>한의원에서</u></span></u><span style='color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'> </span><u><span style='color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'><u>자동차보험으로 진료받을 때 필요한 서류가 있나요?</u></span></u></strong></p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'>접수 시 사고접수번호와 담당자 연락처를 알려주시면 한의원에서 필요한 서류를 직접 발급받습니다.</span><u><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'><u>&#8203;</u></span></u></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><u><strong><span style='color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'><u>- </u></span><span style='color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'><u>자동차보험으로 어떤치료가 가능한가요?</u></span></strong></u></p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'>침, 뜸, 약침, 봉침, 한약(첩약), 추나요법, 한방물리치료 등 증상과 체질에 맞는 치료를 처방합니다.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style='font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><strong>※ </strong></span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">이수한의원에서는  자동차보험치료가 어떤식으로 진행이 되나요?</span></strong></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140603_209/isuhani_14017668248775d3PP_JPEG/%C0%DA%BA%B8.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"383\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rheight: 383px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140603_209/isuhani_14017668248775d3PP_JPEG/%C0%DA%BA%B8.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333A29F237')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140603_209/isuhani_14017668248775d3PP_JPEG/%C0%DA%BA%B8.jpg?type=w3\"></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><strong>※ </strong></span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">이수한의원에서는 자동차보험으로 어떤치료를 받게 되나요?</span></strong></span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; background-color: rgb(199, 241, 70);'><strong><br /></strong></span></p><div align=\"justify\"><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">- 침치료</span></strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'><strong>- 어혈약침 및 봉침치료</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140603_140/isuhani_14017724048954nSkS_JPEG/BAC0%A9%A4_3731522085_20090910213217_4756179866.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"200\" height=\"150\" align=\"right\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); clear: right; rheight: 150px; rwidth: 200px;\" id=\"20140603_140/isuhani_14017724048954nSkS_JPEG/BAC0%A9%A4_3731522085_20090910213217_4756179866.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333A29F237')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140603_140/isuhani_14017724048954nSkS_JPEG/BAC0%A9%A4_3731522085_20090910213217_4756179866.jpg?type=w3\"></div><div align=\"justify\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140603_288/isuhani_1401767739556K3HQr_JPEG/acupuncture-needles-300x184.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"200\" height=\"150\" align=\"left\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); clear: left; rheight: 150px; rwidth: 200px;\" id=\"20140603_288/isuhani_1401767739556K3HQr_JPEG/acupuncture-needles-300x184.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333A29F237')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140603_288/isuhani_1401767739556K3HQr_JPEG/acupuncture-needles-300x184.jpg?type=w3\"> </div><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p align=\"justify\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p><div align=\"justify\"><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">- 추나요법</span></strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">- 한약(첩약)치료</span></strong></span><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140603_189/isuhani_1401773168380oYmpz_JPEG/ChineseHerbs3.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"200\" height=\"150\" align=\"right\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); clear: right; rheight: 150px; rwidth: 200px;\" id=\"20140603_189/isuhani_1401773168380oYmpz_JPEG/ChineseHerbs3.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333A29F237')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140603_189/isuhani_1401773168380oYmpz_JPEG/ChineseHerbs3.jpg?type=w3\"></div><div align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140603_227/isuhani_14017723000308gQiD_JPEG/WO0W4531.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"200\" height=\"150\" align=\"left\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); clear: left; rheight: 150px; rwidth: 200px;\" id=\"20140603_227/isuhani_14017723000308gQiD_JPEG/WO0W4531.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333A29F237')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140603_227/isuhani_14017723000308gQiD_JPEG/WO0W4531.jpg?type=w3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </div><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p align=\"justify\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">- 부항치료</span></strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">- 한방물리치료</span></strong></span></p><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140603_40/isuhani_14017732751190bFEC_PNG/1089ca_86747fcb3a05acf0aae46adc15b371a5_png_srz_970_400_85_22_0_50_1_20_0.png?type=w80_blur\" width=\"200\" height=\"150\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rheight: 150px; rwidth: 200px;\" id=\"20140603_40/isuhani_14017732751190bFEC_PNG/1089ca_86747fcb3a05acf0aae46adc15b371a5_png_srz_970_400_85_22_0_50_1_20_0.png\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333A29F237')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140603_40/isuhani_14017732751190bFEC_PNG/1089ca_86747fcb3a05acf0aae46adc15b371a5_png_srz_970_400_85_22_0_50_1_20_0.png?type=w3\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140603_1/isuhani_1401773715652agjco_JPEG/P6033035.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"200\" height=\"150\" align=\"right\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); clear: right; rheight: 150px; rwidth: 200px;\" id=\"20140603_1/isuhani_1401773715652agjco_JPEG/P6033035.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333A29F237')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140603_1/isuhani_1401773715652agjco_JPEG/P6033035.JPG?type=w3\"></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 243, 145);'><strong>⇒ 가벼운 사고라고 할지라도 후유증이 나타날 수 있습니다.</strong></span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif; background-color: rgb(246, 243, 145);'><strong>\"이정도면 괜찮겠지..\"라고 생각하지 마시고 이수한의원에 내원하셔서 자동차보험으로 치료하세요!</strong></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
